{"tid":1393080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"諗梗辭職全力上場 求意見","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:07:07.000Z","uid":289599,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f99acc658dae23c7b4da5d2e3300e6482677371e","tid":1393080,"uid":289599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"我跟公司做拍野<br />\n份工幾好 返一至五 全公司都黃<br />\n但最近呢個幾月個心完全飛左去運動<br />\n成個腦淨係諗點拆水炮車 點冚催淚彈 點打柒班黑警<br />\n真心唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n我父母年幾前都搬左去美國<br />\n老母明我地香港發生咩事 都冇阻止我去<br />\n但就同我講 如果留係香港太大壓力<br />\n就俾錢我賠錢公司走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係咪應該聽個心講</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">辭職全力勇武？</span>"},{"pid":"c29b355ad6c6381d1329d231ea173f7999808e62","tid":1393080,"uid":73826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"唔好辭<br />\n生活要有其他寄託<br />\n假日出黎戰爭已經好大幫忙<br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"96769552ff3b81933654b9af3d4a253a63b81652","tid":1393080,"uid":260367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c29b355ad6c6381d1329d231ea173f7999808e62","tid":1393080,"uid":73826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"唔好辭<br />\n生活要有其他寄託<br />\n假日出黎戰爭已經好大幫忙<br />\n多謝你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"950fc1e14103df289d681328bc34acd086557f78","tid":1393080,"uid":285371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"和理勇武決一不可，出錢又出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb81c006ac4e8b3f53e04cae6f9ad12be25864f","tid":1393080,"uid":230730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37cc0d5ff1808c8b94186faac8e17736825dca31","tid":1393080,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"無負擔真係好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我間公司好多藍絲<br />\n請珍惜"},{"pid":"1